Package org.melior.client.activemq

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveMQClient
    Implements an easy to use, auto-configuring ActiveMQ client with connection pooling, configurable backoff strategy and automatic object mapping.
    ActiveMQClientBuilder
    Convenience class for building a ActiveMQClient.
    ActiveMQClientConfig
    Configuration parameters for a ActiveMQClient, with defaults.
    Connection
    Implements a wrapper around an ActiveMQ Connection delegate.
    ConnectionFactory
    Implements a factory for persistent ActiveMQ Connection objects.
    ConnectionManager
    Implements a manager for persistent ActiveMQ Connection objects, for connections to ActiveMQ servers.
    Producer
    A wrapper around an ActiveMQ Producer object which makes the Producer persistent.
    Session
    A wrapper around an ActiveMQ Session object which makes the Session persistent.
    TextMessageCreator
    Constructs a new ActiveMQ Message object from a text payload.
